Dialogue: 50,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.21,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{Kaido-sama !}كايدو-ساما
Dialogue: 50,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.72,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{What is it?!\NDon't bother me when I'm drinking!}ما الأمر؟ لا تزعجني عندما احتسي الساكي
Dialogue: 50,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.18,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{No! I didn't mean to!}لا، لم أقصد ذلك
Dialogue: 50,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.31,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{The thing is...}...كل ما في الأمر
Dialogue: 50,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.11,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{What do you want?!}ماذا تريدين؟
Dialogue: 50,0:01:36.95,0:01:39.32,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{It's about Straw Hat.}أود التحدث معك عن قبعة القش
Dialogue: 50,0:01:39.32,0:01:42.54,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{He's on his way to you.}إنه يتجه إليك حاليًا
Dialogue: 50,0:01:42.54,0:01:44.91,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<So what?>What are you getting at?}وماذا في ذلك؟
Dialogue: 50,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.21,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{Listen, keep your hands off him!}اسمع، لا تلمسه
Dialogue: 50,0:01:49.38,0:01:53.63,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{I'm coming to Wano to claim Straw Hat's head myself.}سآتي إلى وانو لقتل قبعة القش بنفسي
Dialogue: 50,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.34,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{Is this some kind of <a >joke?! I refuse!}أتمزحين معي؟ أرفض ذلك
Dialogue: 50,0:01:57.34,0:02:00.09,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{I have no business with you.}الأمر لا يعنيك
Dialogue: 50,0:02:00.93,0:02:06.39,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{I've got to take Straw Hat out, or I'll lose face!}{If I don't personally squash Straw Hat, \N}{my reputation will suffer}{I'll become a laughingstock.}{Zenef: I like the original line "I'll lose face" but it's much shorter than the spoken line.}سأشعر بالعار إن لم أقتل قبعة القش بنفسي
Dialogue: 50,0:02:06.39,0:02:10.23,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{Besides, he has something that I want back!}كما أنني أودّ استعادة شيء أخذه مني
Dialogue: 50,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.94,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{I don't care!}لا أكترث
Dialogue: 50,0:02:12.32,0:02:15.90,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{You still owe me big time, <right>don't you?}أظن أنك تدين لي بمعروف
Dialogue: 50,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.53,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{Owe you?}معروف؟
Dialogue: 50,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.16,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<You remember, don't you?>Don't tell me you've forgotten.}لم تنسَ ذلك، صحيح؟
Dialogue: 50,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.37,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{That was a long time ago!}كان ذلك منذ زمن بعيد
Dialogue: 50,0:02:22.37,0:02:25.24,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<But...}{No matter!}{Even so, it was a <lifetime>lifelong debt.}لا، إنه دين مدى الحياة
Dialogue: 50,0:02:31.00,0:02:37.05,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<I'm the one who's got a grudge against that Straw Hat brat!>I'm the one who'll get even \Nwith that Straw Hat rookie!}أنا من لديه حساب ليصفيه مع ذلك الطفل قبعة القش
Dialogue: 50,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.72,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{So I'm the one who'll kill him!}أنا من سيقتل ذلك الطفل
Dialogue: 50,0:02:39.72,0:02:43.43,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<If you come, I'll kill you too, Linlin!>Show your face, and I'll kill you too, Linlin!}وسأقتلك أيضًا إن جئتِ يا لينلين
Dialogue: 50,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.22,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{I'd like to see you try.<I didn't call to get your permission, I'm just giving you fair warning.>}جرّب ذلك
Dialogue: 50,0:02:45.22,0:02:48.73,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{I'm not asking your permission;\Nthis is merely a courtesy call.}فلم أتصل {عليك}بك لطلب إذنك بل لتحذيرك
Dialogue: 50,0:02:50.60,0:02:54.69,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<Get it>Got that? Straw Hat's head is mine!}أفهمت؟ أنا من سيقطع رأس قبعة القش
Dialogue: 50,0:02:54.69,0:02:58.99,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<Let's try and get along... like we used to!>So let's play nice... for old times' sake!}لنتحد كالأيام الخوالي
Dialogue: 50,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.53,AR-Main,,0,0,5,,{\be3}{Big Mom is on the move!}بيغ مام تتحرك{\an8}
