Dialogue: 50,0:03:09.75,0:03:14.84,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<They don't care about being wiretapped>Don't they care if we overhear?!\NAre they trying to provoke us?}لا يكترثا بالتنصت عليهما، هل يسعيان لاستفزازنا؟
Dialogue: 50,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.92,AR-Main,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{<Let's try and get along...>So let's play nice...}لنتحد كالأيام الخوالي
